Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露妮妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 這可真是美如畫啊 勇鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這麽說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 勇鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳如果打算娶菲麗希亞的話 可不能沾花惹草哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 我在故鄉已經有喜歡的人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之 妳要是敢惹哭我妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等著受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百煉霸王與聖約女武神
