Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹的關系真是復雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點心會被搶去吃 沒事還會被撓癢癢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但妹妹果然還是很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麽
